---
title: Pork Schnitzel and Aioli with Roasted Brussels Sprouts and Mashed Potatoes
description: Schnitzel is a German staple of thinly sliced meat that is breaded and then pan-fried for a quick, delicious weeknight dinner the whole family will love! A dollop of aioli is the perfect schnitzel topper.
